reviewText: Great movie in English, but when I ordered it, I got the clamshell package for Mateo, but inside it was Hechos de Los Apotales, which is excelente, but I wanted Mateo!
Would be awesome if the outer clamshell package matched the product. I just ordered it, and inside was Hechos de los Apostales... which is muy bueno, pero yo quiero Mateo!
FANTASTIC MOVIE OF CHRIST OUR LORD. WORD FOR WORD FROM NIV ALL ACTED OUT. AMAZING !!!! GREAT FOR FAMILY, FRIENDS, NEIGHBORS, GIFTS, OR TITHE.
I recomend this movie its awesome 100% the best ever its the bible but in dvd version
